Stoke City are showing an interest in Sporting Lisbon left winger Diego Capel.

The 26-year-old Spain international is valued at £7million but Stoke are understood to have made an opening offer of around £3.8m.

Manager Mark Hughes also wants Oussama Assaidi from Liverpool but has been quoted £7million for the 25-year-old.

